#: ../../sysadmclient.rst:114
msgid ""
"**Search:** To see if an application is available, enter its name and click "
"the \"binoculars\" icon. Alternately, enter a description. For example, a "
"search for \"browser\" will display software with \"browser\" in the name as"
" well as applications which provide browser functionality, such as Firefox."
